This paper deals with image processing and analysis, specifically focusing on image fusion techniques. The paper discusses feature extraction and introduces three different types of image fusion techniques. These topics are closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), multimedia (cs.MM), graphics (cs.GR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
